      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEART DESIRES (2) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at Maitland over 400m behind Tropical Ethics (23.27) in a Grade 5. The form out of her last race has been franked. Should be very hard to beat this time. FEDERAL UNITED (1) last appeared when too good (23.59) over 400m at this track on December 13. Resumes after finishing fourth (23.59) at this track over 400m six months ago. Tends to go well off this box draw. Overall strike-rate good and can feature with the right run. KALANI MISS (7) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (23.85) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Great chance to atone.",
